# ============================================================================
# NOTES
# ============================================================================

# Pokemon names must be:
#   - Lowercase
#   - No spaces (use hyphens: "mr-mime" not "mr mime")
#   - Match the PokeAPI format

# Pokemon IDs must be:
#   - Between 1 and 1010
#   - Valid Pokemon from the API

# Team size must be:
#   - Between 1 and 6 Pokemon (like a real Pokemon team!)

# After editing, test with:
#   terraform validate
#   terraform plan
